{"tid":2153686,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Xbox Series X 宣布 11 月發售！將有千款大作護航","createTime":"2020-08-12T16:28:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T03:15:54.000Z","uid":212473,"like":6,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6d7750a0ff034692f4b283989680cdbd9d5a4f7d","tid":2153686,"uid":212473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T16:28:08.000Z","msg":"Microsoft 在 12 號於自家網站刊出了一篇文章，宣布 Xbox Series X 將會在今 11 月的時候發售，並在標題表示會有上千款橫跨四個世代的大作替其護航：<br />\n<br />\n橫跨 Xbox ONE 與 Xbox Series X 的新作如 Assassin&rsquo;s Creed Valhalla、Dirt 5、Gears Tactics、人中之龍 6、Watch Dogs：Legion 等作品將支援 Smart Delivery，購買單一般本就能在兩款主機上玩。<br />\n<br />\n獨佔大作 The Medium、Scorn、Tetris Effect：Connected 將會加入 Xbox Game Pass。<br />\n<br />\n40多款現有熱門遊戲例如Destiny 2、Forza Horizo​​n 4、Gears 5、Ori、Wisps of Wisps、Madden NFL 21 將會針對 Xbox Series X 進行優化。<br />\n<br />\n另外，《Halo Infinite》也確認延期至2021年推出，製作方 343 Industries 表示將持續聽取玩家社群的意見並提升遊戲品質，可能是在今年 E3 展上那慘不忍睹的畫面表現而造成的討論度、MEME 四起讓他們終於認知歹誌大條。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.xfastest.com/microsoft/84139/xbox-series-x-%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83-11-%E6%9C%88%E7%99%BC%E5%94%AE%EF%BC%81%E5%B0%87%E6%9C%89%E5%8D%83%E6%AC%BE%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%9C%E8%AD%B7%E8%88%AA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fmicrosoft%2F84139%2Fxbox-series-x-%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583-11-%25E6%259C%2588%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%2594%25AE%25EF%25BC%2581%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%258D%2583%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E8%2588%25AA%2F&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7SF8jviwHHlsaTD6zKFHFMM%3D&h=90b76840\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.xfastest.com/microsoft/84139/xbox-series-x-%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83-11-%E6%9C%88%E7%99%BC%E5%94%AE%EF%BC%81%E5%B0%87%E6%9C%89%E5%8D%83%E6%AC%BE%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%9C%E8%AD%B7%E8%88%AA/</a>"},{"pid":"a1f2d22abe79cc186c36f9d69a5d984f4772d173","tid":2153686,"uid":180401,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T16:31:13.000Z","msg":"一買要買2部 <br />\